{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Join the cutest and most fearsome squad ever!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <strong>Shard Squad</strong>, help a team of elemental creatures save their lands in a thrilling and chaotic adventure filled with monsters and projectiles leaping off your screen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363560/extras/Batalha_Feito_com_o_Clipchamp-export.gif?t=1738952442\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But don\u2019t worry\u2014great challenges come with great allies! The squad is ready to assist you, providing valuable items or even cooking up nutrients to power you up to defeat the toughest bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363560/extras/NPCS__1_.gif?t=1738952442\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Speaking of bosses, brace yourself for a wave of unique creatures constantly testing your skills. And if you manage to overcome them, an even greater calamity awaits at the end of each stage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363560/extras/Boss_Battle_Feito_com_o_Clipchamp.gif?t=1738952442\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Remember: no battle is fought alone! The squad always has each other's backs, and you get to choose who fights by your side, bringing the mechanics you need to overcome vicious hordes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363560/extras/Suporte_Feito_com_o_Clipchamp.gif?t=1738952442\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"b